RelatedSentence: - Armenian parliament approved the bill on special investigation committee by 88 votes for , 32 - against and one abstention .
According to the government plan , in the future the Special Committee will be joined by investigating authorities of other agencies , most likely the State Revenue Committee .
Opposition is categorically against the bill : MP Nikol Pashinyan called it  employment project for young retiree Aghvan Hovsepyan .
